Resource Profile: CH Audit Event for [CH:MHD-1] Document Recipient

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epr-fhir/StructureDefinition/ch-mhd-updatedocumentmetadata-audit-recipient Version: 4.0.1
